    "markdown": {
      "text": "<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_65_144_153_209.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"7%\" /></div>\n\n\n##### WORD MASTER\n\nfriendship - relation between friends\n\nlibrary - A room where books are kept\n\nrestaurant - A place where we eat meals and pay for it\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_66_372_144_442.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"6%\" /></div>\n\n\n##### LET'S TRY\n\nA. Write whether true or false.\n\n1. Tablet is a type of computer.\n\n2. Laptop is a very big computer.\n\n3. Computers can be seen in a mall.\n\n4. Computers can not be our friend.\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_733_476_1080_746.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"29%\" /></div>\n\n\nB. Fill in the blanks using words from the Help-Box.\n\n\n\n<table border=1 style='margin: auto; word-wrap: break-word;'><tr><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'>Help Box</td><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'>computers</td><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'>play</td><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'>big</td><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'>places</td></tr></table>\n\nWe can play with our friends. In the same way we can play with\n\ncomputals also. They can be big or small. They are mostly found at\n\nall places.\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_68_1016_151_1092.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"6%\" /></div>\n\n\n##### LET'S LEARN\n\n## C. Match the following.\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_78_1151_1079_1433.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"84%\" /></div>\n\n\nD. Unjumble the given letters to write meaningful words.\n\n1. MPUCOTRE\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_101_1537_400_1596.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"25%\" /></div>\n\n\n2. PALOPT\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_497_1546_714_1595.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"18%\" /></div>\n\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_846_1444_1056_1592.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"17%\" /></div>\n",
